{"type":"message","id":"efa26de6","parentId":"fae8a92b","timestamp":"2026-05-14T07:28:10.181Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. The pipeline completed:\n1. ✅ 打资源 completed successfully (138.58s)\n2. ✅ 上传CDN completed in 1.18s - though there was a non-fatal 404 error when trying to download a remote file (this happens in 本地测试 mode when the remote file doesn't exist yet, and it falls back to local setup)\n3. The pipeline ended normally\n\nThe 404 error is not a fatal error - it's just trying to download a CDN file from a URL that doesn't exist yet (for a new version). The local test environment was prepared successfully at `D:/cdn_solo\\update\\Android\\Test1\\1.0.41`.\n\nNow I need to send the Feishu message to the group. Let me use the feishu skill to send a message. But first I need to read the feishu skill to know how to send messages.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Pipeline 已完成！构建成功，CDN 上传步骤也已完成（本地测试环境已就绪）。现在去飞书群通知。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_SGUTTLrFTEPPYi3tZGV68655","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\feishu-doc\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1690,"output":280,"cacheRead":32768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34738,"cost":{"input":0.0002366,"output":0.00007840000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000917504,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001232504}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778743687330,"responseId":"77a8719e-0776-4656-a540-c79ee48ac094"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6a81d080","parentId":"efa26de6","timestamp":"2026-05-14T07:28:10.210Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_SGUTTLrFTEPPYi3tZGV68655","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-doc\ndescription: |\n  Feishu document read/write operations. Activate when user mentions Feishu docs, cloud docs, or docx links.\n---\n\n# Feishu Document Tool\n\nSingle tool `feishu_doc` with action parameter for all document operations, including table creation for Docx.\n\n## Token Extraction\n\nFrom URL `https://xxx.feishu.cn/docx/ABC123def` → `doc_token` = `ABC123def`\n\n## Actions\n\n### Read Document\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"read\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\" }\n```\n\nReturns: title, plain text content, block statistics. Check `hint` field - if present, structured content (tables, images) exists that requires `list_blocks`.\n\n### Write Document (Replace All)\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"write\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"content\": \"# Title\\n\\nMarkdown content...\" }\n```\n\nReplaces entire document with markdown content. Supports: headings, lists, code blocks, quotes, links, images (`![](url)` auto-uploaded), bold/italic/strikethrough.\n\n**Limitation:** Markdown tables are NOT supported.\n\n### Append Content\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"append\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"content\": \"Additional content\" }\n```\n\nAppends markdown to end of document.\n\n### Create Document\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"create\", \"title\": \"New Document\", \"owner_open_id\": \"ou_xxx\" }\n```\n\nWith folder:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"create\",\n  \"title\": \"New Document\",\n  \"folder_token\": \"fldcnXXX\",\n  \"owner_open_id\": \"ou_xxx\"\n}\n```\n\n**Important:** Always pass `owner_open_id` with the requesting user's `open_id` (from inbound metadata `sender_id`) so the user automatically gets `full_access` permission on the created document. Without this, only the bot app has access.\n\n### List Blocks\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"list_blocks\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\" }\n```\n\nReturns full block data including tables, images. Use this to read structured content.\n\n### Get Single Block\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"get_block\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"block_id\": \"doxcnXXX\" }\n```\n\n### Update Block Text\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"update_block\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"block_id\": \"doxcnXXX\",\n  \"content\": \"New text\"\n}\n```\n\n### Delete Block\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"delete_block\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"block_id\": \"doxcnXXX\" }\n```\n\n### Create Table (Docx Table Block)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"create_table\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"row_size\": 2,\n  \"column_size\": 2,\n  \"column_width\": [200, 200]\n}\n```\n\nOptional: `parent_block_id` to insert under a specific block.\n\n### Write Table Cells\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"write_table_cells\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"table_block_id\": \"doxcnTABLE\",\n  \"values\": [\n    [\"A1\", \"B1\"],\n    [\"A2\", \"B2\"]\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### Create Table With Values (One-step)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"create_table_with_values\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"row_size\": 2,\n  \"column_size\": 2,\n  \"column_width\": [200, 200],\n  \"values\": [\n    [\"A1\", \"B1\"],\n    [\"A2\", \"B2\"]\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nOptional: `parent_block_id` to insert under a specific block.\n\n### Upload Image to Docx (from URL or local file)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_image\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"url\": \"https://example.com/image.png\"\n}\n```\n\nOr local path with position control:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_image\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"file_path\": \"/tmp/image.png\",\n  \"parent_block_id\": \"doxcnParent\",\n  \"index\": 5\n}\n```\n\nOptional `index` (0-based) inserts the image at a specific position among sibling blocks. Omit to append at end.\n\n**Note:** Image display size is determined by the uploaded image's pixel dimensions. For small images (e.g. 480x270 GIFs), scale to 800px+ width before uploading to ensure proper display.\n\n### Upload File Attachment to Docx (from URL or local file)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_file\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"url\": \"https://example.com/report.pdf\"\n}\n```\n\nOr local path:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_file\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"file_path\": \"/tmp/report.pdf\",\n  \"filename\": \"Q1-report.pdf\"\n}\n```\n\nRules:\n\n- exactly one of `url` / `file_path`\n- optional `filename` override\n- optional `parent_block_id`\n\n## Reading Workflow\n\n1. Start with `action: \"read\"` - get plain text + statistics\n2. Check `block_types` in response for Table, Image, Code, etc.\n3. If structured content exists, use `action: \"list_blocks\"` for full data\n\n## Configuration\n\n```yaml\nchannels:\n  feishu:\n    tools:\n      doc: true # default: true\n```\n\n**Note:** `feishu_wiki` depends on this tool - wiki page content is read/written via `feishu_doc`.\n\n## Permissions\n\nRequired: `docx:document`, `docx:document:readonly`, `docx:document.block:convert`, `drive:drive`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778743690210}}
{"type":"message","id":"8d51862e","parentId":"6a81d080","timestamp":"2026-05-14T07:28:17.095Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to send a message to the Feishu group. But the feishu-doc skill is for document read/write operations, not for sending messages to groups. I need to figure out how to send messages to Feishu groups.\n\nLooking at the subagent context, it says I should \"send a Feishu message to the group\". But I need a way to do this. Let me check if there's a messaging tool available.\n\nActually, looking at the tools available, I don't see a specific \"feishu message\" tool. But since I'm spawned from a feishu channel session, I might need to return the result as text that the main agent will deliver to the group.\n\nWait, the subagent context says:\n\"Only use the `message` tool when explicitly instructed to contact a specific external recipient; otherwise return plain text and let the main agent deliver it\"\n\nBut I don't have a `message` tool in my available tools. Let me check what tools I have... I have:\n- edit, exec, image, memory_get, memory_search, process, read, sessions_yield, update_plan, video_generate, web_fetch, web_search, write\n\nNo feishu message tool. So I'll return the plain text result and the main agent will deliver it.\n\nActually wait, looking more carefully at the \"Group Chats\" section of AGENTS.md, and the subagent context says \"Your session: agent:main:subagent:4819e1bb-42fe-4f3a-b00c-9259f6a104a6\" with \"Requester channel: feishu\".\n\nI think the subagent just needs to report back the completion status and it will be delivered to the group. Let me just complete my task and report the result clearly.\n\nLet me summarize what happened:\n\n1. ✅ Unity 热更流水线执行完成\n2. ✅ 打资源完成 (138.58s)\n   - 3 个包全部构建成功：DefaultPackage/1.1.067, CommonPackage/1.1.065, SoloPackage/1.1.063\n   - Unity引擎打包成功\n   - 构建结果验证成功\n3. ✅ 上传CDN完成 (1.18s)\n   - 本地测试环境已准备就绪: D:/cdn_solo\\update\\Android\\Test1\\1.0.41\n   - ⚠️ 有非致命 404 错误（远程 CDN 文件未找到，本地模式正常回退）\n\nThe 404 error is a known non-fatal issue in local test mode. The pipeline completed successfully.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"流水线执行完毕，结果总结如下：\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 0514 热更流水线执行完成\n\n**时间:** 2026/5/14 15:23 ~ 15:26\n\n### 1️⃣ 打资源 ✅ (138.58s)\n- DefaultPackage/1.1.067 ✅\n- CommonPackage/1.1.065 ✅  \n- SoloPackage/1.1.063 ✅\n- Unity引擎打包成功\n- 构建结果验证成功\n\n### 2️⃣ 上传CDN ✅ (1.18s)\n- 本地测试环境已准备就绪: `D:/cdn_solo\\update\\Android\\Test1\\1.0.41`\n- ⚠️ 非致命 404 错误（远程 CDN 文件首次不存在，本地模式正常回退）\n\n**请主人或兵王确认后可在群里通知：**\n`<at user_id=\"ou_fc5144301797fb813a1fee33e1130ac3\">兵王(周以天)</at> <at user_id=\"ou_e0151fb79bfe816bb40c8754c709d046\">dice(赵乾)</at> 0514流水线更新完成`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1362,"output":819,"cacheRead":34688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36869,"cost":{"input":0.00019068,"output":0.00022932,"cacheRead":0.000971264,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0013912640000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778743690211,"responseId":"a311cdab-85cb-43a6-b1aa-62274d38b477"}}
